<L>__{exterior grounds near caldwell house sun up}
<A>__{arly is seated on the shaft of an old wagon. the first rays of the morning sun streak through the trees across her as she smiles wistfully down at the antics of a little woodchuck cavorting on the ground close to her. in a moment rocklin comes into view in the b.g. he spots arly, who has her back to him, and walks over. his approach frightens the woodchuck away, and turns arly's head toward him. neither has anything to say. now rocklin sits beside arly, but faces the other way.}
